@startuml AD_D02_Add_Update_Medical_Record

title AD_D02 — Add / Update Medical Record

|Doctor|
|System|

|Doctor|

note
  Prerequisites:
  - Doctor is authenticated
  - Target patient is assigned to this doctor
  - Patient record exists in system
end note

start

:Open patient profile\nfrom patient list;

|System|

:Retrieve and display full medical record:\n- Past diagnoses\n- Prescriptions\n- Test results\n- Treatment plans\n- Allergies\n- IVF cycle entries\n(sorted chronologically);

|Doctor|

:Review existing entries\nfor clinical context;
:Click "Add Entry";
:Select entry type;

if (Entry type?) then (Clinical Note)
  :Complete clinical note fields;

else (Diagnosis)
  :Complete diagnosis fields\n(ICD code, description, date);

else (Prescription)
  :Complete prescription fields\n(drug, dose, frequency, duration);

else (Treatment Plan Update)
  :Complete treatment plan\nupdate fields;
endif

|Doctor|

if (Upload supporting file?) then (yes)
  :Attach supporting file\n(scan image, report);

  |System|

  if (File valid?) then (no)
    :Show file validation error;
    |Doctor|
    :Correct and re-attach;
    |System|
  else (yes)
  endif
else (no)
endif

|Doctor|

:Review entry before saving;

|System|

if (All required fields complete?) then (no)
  :Highlight missing fields;\nBlock submission;
  |Doctor|
  :Complete missing fields;
  |System|
else (yes)
endif

:Save entry as immutable record;\nTimestamp + doctor ID;
:Display updated medical record;

|Doctor|

:View saved entry\nin patient record;

stop

@enduml
